[I] A screen ruler and color measurement tool

[T] KRuler is an on-screen ruler for measuring pixels. Position the 0 at your
[T] starting point and measure the precise pixel distance between the starting
[T] point and your cursor.

[U] https://apps.kde.org/kruler/

